author: Inside Edition
description: These teens were fearless in stressful situations. In 2022, three teens stepped in to help a family after they saw smoke coming from a house while driving by. In 2019, a teen was a hero after stepping in to help when a pit bull escaped a neighbor's home and attacked a 6-year-old boy. In 2018, 15-year-old Anthony Borges was shot five times after stepping in to save the lives of his classmates when a shooter opened fire at his school. Inside Edition Digital's Andrea Swindall has more.
title: Teens Who Were Fearless In Stressful Situations

author: Inside Edition
description: A cafe in Germany is really testing customers' limits with its menu options, many of which include insects. Grasshoppers, crickets, and mealworms are included in many dishes. Cook Martin Baumgarten says during the pandemic he had a lot of extra time to experiment with new ingredients. Inside Edition Digital’s Mara Montalbano has more.
title: Insects Featured Prominently On Cafe Menu In Germany
